@startuml
title Staff Member Class State Machine Diagram

state Unassigned
state AssignedToClient
state AssignedToCampaign
state Unemployed
state Archived

[*] --> LoggedIn
LoggedIn --> Assign : assignStaffMember
Assign --> AssignedToClient : assignedToClient
Assign --> AssignedToCampaign : assignedToCampaign
AssignedToClient --> SwitchAssignment : switchAssignment
AssignedToCampaign --> SwitchAssignment : switchAssignment
SwitchAssignment --> Unassigned : switchAssignment
Unassigned --> RemoveAssignment : removeAssignment
RemoveAssignment --> Unemployed : removeAssignment
Unemployed --> LeaveJob : leaveJob
LeaveJob --> Unemployed
Unemployed --> Archive : archiveRecord
Archive --> Archived : COMPLETION_EVENT
Archived --> [*] : COMPLETION_EVENT
@enduml
